{"tid":593031,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個日文既迷思","createTime":"2018-03-14T16:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T11:06:11.000Z","uid":76542,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"05d9860992d2f3698236b5585a2df3ec78ad6039","tid":593031,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n你地一定聽過日本人講<br />\nわたし(watashi)會講成(wadashi)<br />\nですか(desuka)會講成(desuga)<br />\nました(mashita)會講成(mashida)<br />\n等等<br />\n但唱日文歌又會變返正常<br />\n<br />\n其實當中係有原因。<br />\n<br />\n日本人係講日文方面其實好懶<br />\n因為日文好多時單字都比較長<br />\n例如廣東話 多謝 2粒字<br />\n日文就ありがとうございます 10粒字。。<br />\n令到用日文時<br />\n要表達一個意思要講好多字(好多人都知)<br />\n所以日本人鍾意將日文講得比較簡便<br />\n係拉麵鋪有時會聽到店員講<br />\nありがとうございます既時候<br />\n會hea到將ありがとうござい縮埋一舊變成2,3隻字讀<br />\n然後大大聲講ます<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係想務求快d表達到個意思<br />\n<br />\n咁講左咁耐關<br />\nわたし(watashi)會講成(wadashi)<br />\n咩事呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實就係因為簡便既關係。<br />\n<br />\nta 係送氣音(放隻手係口讀出黎有氣噴)<br />\nda 係不送氣音(放隻手係口讀出黎冇氣噴)<br />\n日本人習慣性咁將送氣音讀成不送氣音<br />\n只係因為讀送氣音比較哂力氣。。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔係日本人讀錯，而係日常生活中<br />\n佢地已經自動將d送氣音讀成不送氣音<br />\n講完。"},{"pid":"3969b7558fa0bbb499f919c98b1c7161fc2b7aaa","tid":593031,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"吐媽途 吐尾途"},{"pid":"0daf1e4cafd00315d4a9a62aadab088a034aad43","tid":593031,"uid":125255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"日本人成日講ます<br />\n聽落好順耳變左英文加s 咁"},{"pid":"3d6959883a8e15e60dd4fd71e4f237a8ae9f13e7","tid":593031,"uid":192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"咪姐係PTK原則⋯⋯"},{"pid":"917da9e9372b0af9e3e46598dde89d124948e50c","tid":593031,"uid":162095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"咁關你中間講個段嘢咩事"},{"pid":"3e53c2f250b904c0aa1ee97d8cf0483bda278234","tid":593031,"uid":26266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"依家初初學日文都有依個問題<br />\n唔係好分到か定が"},{"pid":"05ed681b580cef743a641ee86d365c90909f6666","tid":593031,"uid":153193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"熱菇熱菇"},{"pid":"4fbd80f81400b62b37e3ca1bd14e493f6fcdccde","tid":593031,"uid":76542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"917da9e9372b0af9e3e46598dde89d124948e50c","tid":593031,"uid":162095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"咁關你中間講個段嘢咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"類比嘛，用大家都認知既野帶出左日本人講野會簡單化先<br />\n之後一野套落去氣音同無氣音度。<br />\n否則有d人未學過日文但又好奇既可能唔明"},{"pid":"b82c02ca1c40b8cf12e3604302aafe66e7828e72","tid":593031,"uid":2462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"記得學過 長い (nagai) 中間要有ng音<br />\n發音類似 &ldquo;na挨i&rdquo;<br />\n但現實好似冇人咁讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c034eee39ee33b935d6e7e0588428f6f0dc108","tid":593031,"uid":27129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82c02ca1c40b8cf12e3604302aafe66e7828e72","tid":593031,"uid":2462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:20:16.000Z","msg":"記得學過 長い (nagai) 中間要有ng音<br />\n發音類似 &ldquo;na挨i&rdquo;<br />\n但現實好似冇人咁讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"多數係年紀大嗰啲人先會讀ガ行讀到有鼻音"},{"pid":"2e983b6e02aae6267b0c084e4a4a15088906675c","tid":593031,"uid":143383,"like":1,"disli